clusive package name while additionally providing the following:\r\n\r\n* libignition-common2-core(-dev)\r\n* libignition-common2-av(-dev)\r\n* libignition-common2-events(-dev)\r\n* libignition-common2-graphics(-dev)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>ign-common2 now has separate components for events, graphics, and av, but we are not providing separate install packages.</p>\n<p>We could consider keeping <code>libignition-common2-dev</code> as the all inclusive package name while additionally providing the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>libignition-common2-core(-dev)</li>\n<li>libignition-common2-av(-dev)</li>\n<li>libignition-common2-events(-dev)</li>\n<li>libignition-common2-graphics(-dev)</li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2018-08-21T19:44:35.500237+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2018-08-21T19:44:35.500237+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1}